      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     move  "U"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rig
                     go to acc-tpm-rig-999.
       acc-tpm-rig-360.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
