           perform   vis-tpm-rig-000      thru vis-tpm-rig-999        .
       acc-tpm-rig-365.
           move      "D"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rig      .
           go to     acc-tpm-rig-999.
       acc-tpm-rig-375.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-nok-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-nok-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rig
                             go to acc-tpm-rig-999
                     else    go to acc-tpm-rig-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
