      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura tabella numerazioni [vdpprt]            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "GT"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/vdp/num/ioc/obj/invdpprt"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rn-vdp-prt             .
