      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to att-vdp-ndo-000.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Unlock                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RL"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/vdp/num/ioc/obj/invdpndo"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rn-vdp-ndo             .
