      *                      * Valore in uscita                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rn-vdp-ndo-num-doc   to   w-att-vdp-ndo-num      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     att-vdp-ndo-999.
       att-vdp-ndo-300.
