      *                  * Se numero documento passato non a zero      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se numero documento passato minore o u- *
      *                      * guale a quello letto : uscita           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-att-vdp-ndo-num    >    w-att-vdp-ndo-nsv
                     go to att-vdp-ndo-320.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Unlock                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RL"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/vdp/num/ioc/obj/invdpndo"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rn-vdp-ndo             .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Azzeramento nuovo numero documento  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-att-vdp-ndo-new      .
           go to     att-vdp-ndo-999.
       att-vdp-ndo-320.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
