           move      w-att-vdp-ndo-nsv    to   w-att-vdp-ndo-wnu      .
           add       1                    to   w-att-vdp-ndo-wpr      .
           if        w-att-vdp-ndo-wpr    =    zero
                     move  1              to   w-att-vdp-ndo-wpr      .
           if        w-att-vdp-ndo-prg    =    w-att-vdp-ndo-wpr
