      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se risposta positiva            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Aggiornamento numerazione   *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Numero                  *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      w-att-vdp-ndo-num    to   w-att-vdp-ndo-wnu      .
           move      w-att-vdp-ndo-saa    to   w-att-vdp-ndo-wsa      .
           move      w-att-vdp-ndo-dpz    to   w-att-vdp-ndo-wdz      .
